your_project/
├── app.py                   # Main Python application (Flask routes)
├── static/                  
│   └── css/
│       └── bootstrap.min.css # Bootstrap CSS (if using local files)
│   └── js/
│       └── bootstrap.bundle.min.js # Bootstrap JS (if using local files)
│   └── images/
│       └── product_image1.jpg # Example product images (placeholders)
├── templates/
│   └── base.html             # Base HTML template with Bootstrap navigation and structure
│   └── index.html            # Home page template (extending base.html)
│   └── products.html         # Products page template (example)
│   └── cart.html             # Cart page template (example)
├── requirements.txt          # List of dependencies (Flask, etc.)
└── README.md                 # Project overview and setup instructions
